Available make commands:
* `install`:	      Installs the app via bundle
* `migrate`:	      Updates/creates the database to reflect the app's schema
* `test`:	      Run the default unit and integration test suites
* `unit`:	      Run the default unit test suite
* `integration`:      Run the default integration test suite
* `smoke`:	      Run the smoke test suite (fast subset of integration tests)
* `meta-test`:	      Run the tests for the test helpers
* `integration-all`:  Run all not-skipped integration tests
* `test-all`:	      Run all unit tests and not-skipped integration tests
* `server`:	      Start the development server
* `lint`:	      Run the Rubocop linter
* `help`:	      Print this message
